strings.Value: "What, you thought I was going to bite the dust? No way!"
"No one beats me. I always survive. Always."
"I got really scared when I saw you fall. Please try to be more careful next time!"
"That's nothing more than brazen vanity. Give up your pride, Amiri, and accept the inevitability of the end!"
"I admire your strength of spirit, Amiri. I wish I had the same."
"You're so obsessed in battle! Your eyes shine and your cheeks are on fire! The look on your face in the heat of battle â€“ it makes me wish I'd been a painter!"
"Amiri is almost Hero! Strong as beast! When you die, can I have your stabber?"
"You are a good fighter, but please, don't sadden me with visions of your early death."
